metadata.description:
The Rug Radio NFT is a Utility NFT that yields token based on the scarcity of the rug. The longer you hold the utility NFT, the more tokens you will receive.

Tokens yield per day:

Rare 1 & 2 = 11, Scarce 1 & 2 = 7, Standard = 5

To learn more about the RugRadio ecosystem, join our Discord or visit http://rug.fm/
metadata.name: Rug Radio: Standard
